By":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415157004e3f59c3c935144f6d7aa34748dd4ae2","tid":1848134,"uid":254813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd1c56ff8270c9a0931810cf8e14874b23cc66d8","tid":1848134,"uid":175866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"休息日吖"},{"pid":"8af530affbbe88bdc737591a0dc9780f4be9908e","tid":1848134,"uid":175866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"問1.\t僱主可否強迫僱員一星期工作七天而不給予僱員休息日 ﹖ <br />\n答1.\t不可以。凡按連續性合約受僱的僱員，每7天可享有1天休息日。 <br />\n除了因機器或工廠設備發生故障或任何緊急事故，否則僱主不可要求僱員在休息日工作。在這 些例外情況下，僱主必須另定休息日。另定休息日須安排在原定休息日後的30天之內。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7a43b6740ed962dc0f01fff116b2a1338a96a2","tid":1848134,"uid":254813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8af530affbbe88bdc737591a0dc9780f4be9908e","tid":1848134,"uid":175866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"問1.\t僱主可否強迫僱員一星期工作七天而不給予僱員休息日 ﹖ <br />\n答1.\t不可以。凡按連續性合約受僱的僱員，每7天可享有1天休息日。 <br />\n除了因機器或工廠設備發生故障或任何緊急事故，否則僱主不可要求僱員在休息日工作。在這 些例外情況下，僱主必須另定休息日。另定休息日須安排在原定休息日後的30天之內。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"咪即係硬食！唔同意唔洗有好日子過！"},{"pid":"b0df82b7cf358c6b3217c5e27d760f596d8c6492","tid":1848134,"uid":172472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23e3bc4d5005f4a1edb61a4b24125a87349f5017","tid":1848134,"uid":214475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa77d92d979fd4d35c084c680dc0d0110ce5f5b3","tid":1848134,"uid":172472,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd5b4e3fe21201aeee48a18f6c540b238547cc72","tid":1848134,"uid":101909,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:16:49.000Z","msg":"可以，AL幾時放係公司決定"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n<br />\n要雙方同意<br />\n<br />\n「年假日期應由僱主在徵詢僱員或其代表的意見後指定」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"你唔同意 可以唔洗返工啦 898 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"原則上可以去勞工處告公司<br />\n<br />\n（純討論）"},{"pid":"d8ed733fb6706b14e63b47fe726ce5b822c503a0","tid":1848134,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:39:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請幫手入去比正評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=fb3ee9ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=18d93899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/?d=n<br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=3941f2e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底<br />\n<br />\n最近口罩同N95 都賣曬，部分手足屋企口罩已經就黎用盡，今日同大家介紹下可以防沙士+TG嘅濾罐同濾棉。第一，係for 用曬/買唔到口罩嘅手足，第二係希望方便大家一次過買齊發夢+出街嘅裝備，就算沙士完左，自用送禮都可以繼續名貴大方。<br />\n<br />\nN95/R95/P95 口罩基本上係particulate respirator, 外科口罩防嘅係飛沫粒子，即係我地用防毒面具代替，就要裝particulate filter，換言之，就係濾棉！<br />\n<br />\n濾棉最高級別就係P100，防油性+非油性粒子，即係TG（油性）同埋病毒都可以防，型號包括2091, 2097, 2297, 6035（只有英國製）,7093 等等，而60926等等嘅6092X 系列濾罐，因為內置P100 濾棉，所以一樣ok <br />\n其中，6053 同 7093 棉係防水的，清潔消毒會較方便，而60926表面亦有膠盒。<br />\n<br />\n有強國人做過測試，係北京霧霾毒氣之下，3M 2091 用左十一日過濾能力都係跌左1%，手足請自行考慮幾耐換一次。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 大log買亦有便，大家可以組團買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.au%2F3M%2Fen_AU%2Fcompany-au%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B8711017%2B3294471754%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=64da3401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com%2F3M%2Fen_US%2Fcompany-us%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B3294776429%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=7bedac88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年沙士，淘大嘅清理人員就係用2091棉+600X 罐（罐理論上唔洗，應該係防佢地嘅清潔同消毒藥水）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如何清潔防毒面具可參考依段片，有教disinfection，主要都係漂白水同消毒劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=f9300a47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n清潔步驟：<br />\n入到屋企唔好除裝備住，用酒精紙巾抹左面具同濾棉/罐表面先，跟住抹埋手再洗手（點解又要酒精又要洗手係有原因的），跟住就除面罩，再跟番片入面嘅教學清潔<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n防毒面具方面，建議大家買/用6800 或者其他包曬成塊面嘅款式，咁樣就唔洗帶眼罩，一舊野保護曬成塊面，最安全。因為你戴半面+眼罩，咁就多舊野清潔，同埋部分眼罩封唔曬，冇咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n型號方面，全面嘅建議大家買6800，順便擋埋橡膠子彈，半面嘅就買7502/ 6500，兩款手足都表示舒適度幾高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=bca8f0e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液</span>"},{"pid":"9c794e63c54b4681560e2a59a261f325b3fc3fde","tid":1848134,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:11:35.000Z","msg":"冇名, 即係我炒你啦"}]}